entries.quest_destroy_d: Destroy Blacksun Hunters, Venomrazors, and Bloodstalkers.
entries.quest_location_d: 'Han solo has had a few run-ins with the bounty hunters on Ord Mantell. Skorr has come close to tagging the infamous smuggler, having set up a trap for him by kidnapping Princess Leia and Luke Skywalker and holding them as bait at a stellar energy station on the Ten Mile Plateau of Ord Mantell.'
entries.split_quest_alert: Dartas Pytin: <Pilot! One of their base commanders are making a run for it! Get him before he makes it to the base!>
entries.title: The Trinity: Dual Moons
entries.title_d: 'We're staging our final attack. In order to make a successful run against the Black Sun headquarters, the Darkveil Eclipse, we need to take out the Dual Moons; the two bases on either side of the hub. This way, when the Black Sun request assistance, there will be no one to help them.'
